      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BOOKALOO (5) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (31.04) in a Grade 4/5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Will find this more suitable and can atone. AILEEN'S SHINE (2) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by half a length at Angle Park in a handy 31.05 beating Buffy's No Angel. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from six starts. Should be in this for a long way. SEBON PRINCE (4) was below best latest but did hit the frame in quick time two back when second (22.94) at this track in a Other. Well placed here and can atone this time. VILLAIN OF MAGIC (7) is new here but cannot be left out.",
